Class EPSCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • manito.eft.interfaces.EPSCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable
    public class EPSCard
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Serializable
    Entity class for holding details relating to a Credit or Debit Card.

      • getCategory

        public int getCategory()
        Get the Category of card.

        Supported categories: 

           CREDIT           standard credit card
   DEBIT            standard debit card
   PURCHASING       corporate purchasing/procurement card
   FUEL             standard fuel card
   BUNKERING        volumetric fuel card
   LOYALTY          loyalty/points card
   LOCAL_ACCOUNT    merchant local payment card
   OPEN_VALUE       stored value card - open/programmable value
   PRESET_VALUE     stored value card - fixed preset value
   EBT_FOOD         EBT Food Stamps
   EBT_CASH         EBT Cash account
        Returns:
        result

        public int getEntryMode()
        Get the Means by which card data was entered.

        Supported operations: 

           MANUAL       PAN manually entered
   MSR          card swiped on MSR
   ICC          card inserted in chip reader
   RFI          card waved past a contactless reader
   SCAN         card details scanned (barcode reader)
   STORED       card details recreated from stored data
